    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this fantastic find! This vehicle is in great condition and has been clearly well-loved and maintained. It drives smoothly and looks sharp, with just the minor signs of character you'd expect from a reliable, high-quality pre-owned car. It\u2019s a wonderful opportunity to own a top-tier vehicle that\u2019s ready for many more miles of adventure!",
