    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for those who need functional transportation. The engine and transmission are in working order, though the car exhibits noticeable cosmetic wear on both the interior and exterior, including some minor scratches and faded upholstery. It has been maintained regularly to ensure it remains roadworthy, but it lacks the polish of a newer or better-kept model. A solid choice for a daily driver if you aren't concerned with perfection.",
      "price": 25000.0,
